    <h1>Keyword Mapping</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of assigning one primary keyword to each page on your site, documented in a spreadsheet. <strong>Prevents keyword cannibalization</strong>, guides on-page optimisation, and ensures your content covers the right queries without internal competition.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
